Wilmuth Merkyl https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wilmuth_Merkyl 0 Wilmuth John Merkyl (June 2, 1885 – May 1, 1954) was an American stage and screen actor popular in early silent films. On stage he had also been a singer in light operettas. He was born in Iowa and died in California.
